      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been sitting here at the edge of the cliffs in santorini for like three hours. it's beautiful, i guess. but it feels like i've checked every box on the list. i've seen the sights, i've done the things... and now i just feel like the itinerary is finished. like there's nowhere left to actually go.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
