      "content": "i don't think i want to \"create a new narrative.\" that sounds like more work. more walking, more luggage, more trying to find meaning in places that don't care if i'm there or not. when the tour is over, you usually just check out and go home. but i don't feel like going home. i just feel like the trip is done and i'm ready for the final exit. does that even make sense? that i just want to finish the journey?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
